But, firstly you need to fix the tea set so you can pour tea into the cups, then place delicious cupcakes on your tray! You can try to match different dresses, accessories and hairstyle, design a new beautiful style princess! Enjoy!

description: Move the obstacles and orbits as long as you can! You have to help the man run around the circle for as long as possible. But many different obstacles appear in his way and you have to help him jump by touching or clicking on the screen and then moving from under them. You will lose if you hit one of the obstacles and then your final score is calculated based on the number of obstacles that you have dodged.

title: Hop Hero
description: Hop Hero is a funny flyppy Owl Html 5 game. You can open the walls by collecting gems. You can use gems to buy new owl yet. Enjoy!

title: Candy Rush 2
description: Candy Rush 2 is landscape puzzle Match 3 game with colorful and beautiful graphics, collect three or more of the same candy. Enjoy!

title: Snake Blast
description: Snake Blast inspired by classic snake game with colorful and modern graphics. get score and avoid the enemy.

title: Shoot Me
description: Shoot Me is a responsive shooting HTML5 game. Shoot down the sticky bottles off the heads of cute and smiling characters. Watch out the heads! Enjoy!

title: Zombie Dodge
description: Zombie Dodge is a fast-pased Html game. Control your little zombie to escape fire balls and other traps dropping from sky. Survive as long time as you can. Enjoy!

title: E-Basket Ball
description: E- Basket Ball is a simple and funny basketball shooting game of HTML5. The goal in the game is to score as much as possible. You have 10+ basketballs to do so. Each time you miss a hit, a ball is deducted. With the score you can unlock 15 different ball skins. Enjoy!

title: Swift Cats
description: Cat vs Rats! Many mice robots invaded the land of cats. All led by the King and Queen Mouse. But the fast cats defend themselves using their main quality: Speed!  There are still super cute kittens and 21 amazing levels. Enjoy!

title: T-Rex Runner
description: The T-Rex has to run, but you must get rid of many traps, such as cacti and pterodactyls. T-Rex Runner is a game based on another famous and very entertaining. But the T-Rex Runner is different, with excellent graphics and two color options. A black and white option, as the original game. And another color option, with amazing color. Enjoy!

title: Girls Fashion Boutique
description: Hi, girl, open the boutique boxes! You will find most hipster clothes, shoes, accessories and bags, pick the one you favorite! Have fun!

description: Hi, girl, let's go shopping together with Anna. In style fashion dresses store, shoes store, fancy jewelry store, boutique shop, you can buy everything you want in these stores , and then go to the hair salon to design a new hairstyle. Oh, you have a new look! Have a nice day!

title: Magic Emeralds
description: Magic Emeralds is a match 3 puzzle Html 5 game. You need to match minimum 3 same objects to earn score. Enjoy!

title: Danger Sense
description: It's your mission that to dodge meteors and collect coins. You can upgrade your character in this Html 5 game. Put new records in survival. Use the arrow keys on the keyboard or press the buttons on the screen to control the character. Have fun!

title: Mega Runner
description: It's time to train your reflexes in a side scrolling Html5 game. Tap to control your hero. Keep out of the spikes and finish the levels. Enjoy!

title: Panic Drop
description: This is an addictive Html 5 adventure game. Avoid the platfroms and collect balls as many as you can. Enjoy!

title: Rain Of Arrows
description: How long can your hero survive? Press and tap the screen to send the hero. Avoid those arrows drop from the clouds. Enjoy!

title: Correct Math
description: It's time to practice your numeracy skills. Choose the correct answer as soon as possible before time runs out. Have fun!

title: Number Jump
description: Our main character wants to reach the sun and there is only one way to do this! Jump on numbers in the proper order and reach the sun! If he jumps on a wrong cloud (number), he falls but won’t lose, he can jump again on the clouds and he will win the game when he reaches the sun. In 'Number Jump', you will become familiar with numbers’ shapes, names and order by seeing and listening to them in their proper order. Enjoy!

title: Princess Sauna Room
description: Rapunzel is going to the sauna spa therapy with Ariel and Anna. Please help Rapunzel prepare for the sauna spa. Firstly, taking a refreshing shower, shaving armpit, take off the jewelry and then changing into a more appropriate outfit. Now, everything is ready! It's time to relax! Enjoy!

description: Congratulations! Disney princesses are going to graduate from college. Tonight the school will hold a grand graduation party, Elsa, Anna, Rapunzel intend to go to the prom together. Now, they are preparing for the party. They need to pick a beautiful dress, the right shoes and match with accessories. Finally, don't forget to design a fashion hairstyle. Enjoy!

title: Inside Out Disgust Throat Surgery
description: Oh, god, it's too bad! Inside Out Disgust's throat is seriously infected. You are her family doctor, please treat her throat infection using medical tools. Eliminate bugs, clean up her throat and use the cool laser to kill any remaining germs. Disgust will be feeling better in no time, thanks!

title: Frozen Anna Braids Design
description: Anna wants to change her hairstyle, can you help give her a makeover? Firstly, you need to wash her hair with shampoo and hair conditioner and then  design a new hairdo for her. A long bob hairstyle or a long hairdo with fancy curls, which one is more fashionable? Make full use of the tools like straighter and curlers to create a fabulous hairstyle. When you finish her new hairdo, choose some cute accessories to make the hairstyle even cuter. Have fun!

title: Adventure Man
description: Run through the forest and escape the dangers. For playing this game, you can use touch in mobile devices and mouse in computer. Enjoy!

title: Block Snake
description: Here is a addictive casual Html 5 game for you! Easy to play. You can spend time to play with your block snake. The more the snake eats, the longer it grows. There are 6 levels. Have a good time.

description: In the game you need to jump from one step to another and avoid enemy blocks. The speed increases as time passes which makes game harder and harder.

title: Crazy Jump

title: Zombie Smash

Let's help them make this day even more unforgettable by giving them super beautiful graduation looks. Choose what the three best friends are going to wear and have fun trying on different robes, shoes and bachelor caps. Design a beautiful graduation outfit for each of them. Have fun!

title: Ariel And Prince Underwater Kissing
description: A funny kissing game, please help mermaid Ariel and prince Eric kiss secretly. Don't be caught by Ursula and other fishes in the sea.

description: Monster Ball is a cool and funny Html 5 fast-paced game. Go on a FUN monster hunting, throw your monster ball and catch them all! Tap on the ground to move and tap the ball to throw. Enjoy!

description: This is a Html 5 game where you have to survive. Collect the ammos and money, get stronger, upgrade their performance. You will  get achievements if you can Kill 100, 1000 and 10,000 zombies. Have fun!

title: Numeric Puzzle

description: Tap to fly and keep the bird to avoid from obstacle.

Are you ready to show off your fashion skills? Help her makeup and pick the most beautiful outfit for her. Don't forget to complete her looks by giving her some fashion accessories. Have fun!

In each equation, the elementary arithmetic is missing and you have to choose the right one based on the numbers and answer and complete the equation. When your 60 seconds end, your score is calculated based on the number of your correct and wrong answers. So be quick and do your best to correctly answer as many questions as you can.

title: Crazy Match 3
description: Crazy Match 3 is a puzzle game that you need to match 3 or more same objects by drawing a line as long as possible. Enjoy new bright and colorful graphics and nice music!

title: Shoot The Aliens

title: Duck Shoot
description: Duck Shoot is an awesome shooting Html 5 game based on the amusement parks. You have to hit the ducks and monsters. But beware of hitting the wrong duck! Have fun!

title: Garden Match 3
description: There are so many cute crops becoming ripe in the mysterious Garden. Collect them by drawing a line to match minimum 3 same crops. Have a good time!

title: Ninja Run

How much you will be able to run? Be careful because in your way will be dangerous jumps, thorns and bombs. Prove that you are the best ninja!

title: Puzzle Block

title: Square Run
description: Square Run is a HTML 5 infinite run game. Simple to play. Control a square to run as long as possible and crack a record!

You are Elsa and Anna's wedding stylist, help them to become the most beautiful bride sisters. Choose the wedding dresses, make up for them and design the right hairstyles. Have fun!

description: Elsa is pregnant! Her figure becomes bad, but she still wants herself is a beautiful pregnant woman. Firstly, give herself a bath, and then make a facial spa, finally put on a beautiful dress. Enjoy!

But winter is so cold, they need warm clothes. Hats, gloves, scarfs, coats, lovely and warm. In the game, please help the ponies show winter fashion.

title: Baby Stunning Fashion
description: Design a stunning fashion baby! In the dress up game you can try three different styles for baby: polka dots, candy colors and denim fashion. Have fun!   Control: Use Mouse to play.

description: A karting racing HTML5 game, your goal is to get first of 5 laps. Each opponent has individual intelligence and they will do everything to prevent you from winning the match!
